title: Gymea Shopping Village to become more pedestrian friendly (Sutherland Shire Council)
text: ( Source : Sutherland Shire Council ) Published On 16 October 2015 at 03:00 PM Sutherland Shire Council and Roads and Maritime Services ( RMS ) are implementing a 40km/h speed limit through Gymea Shopping Village to increase pedestrian safety
